                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.34/169a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Warren</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="91" xml:id="d531fn91">See penultimate paragraph for
                        instructions to repeat to Peking; also last paragraph concerning repetition
                        to the Ambassadors in Great Britain (no. 127), France (no. 131), and Italy
                        (no. 56).</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-05-04T14:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 4, 1922—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>37. I am today handing to the Japanese, British, French and Italian
                    representatives here an <hi rend="italic">aide memoire</hi> to the following
                    effect:</p>
                <p>[Here follows text of <hi rend="italic">aide-mémoire</hi> printed <hi
                        rend="italic">supra.</hi>]</p>
                <p>You will communicate the above to the Foreign Office and request an expression of
                    its views.</p>
                <pb facs="0869" n="749" xml:id="pg_749"/>
                <p>Repeat to Peking for its information, omitting last sentence.</p>
                <p>(Same <hi rend="italic">mutatis mutandis</hi> to London as no. 127, to Paris as
                    no. 131, to Rome as no. 56.)</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
